In [59]:
month = np.where(month == 1, "Jan", month)
month = np.where(month == '2', "Feb", month)
month = np.where(month == '3', "Mar", month)
month = np.where(month == '4', "Apr", month)
month = np.where(month == '5', "Jun", month)
month = np.where(month == '6', "July", month)

plt.figure(figsize=(15,20));
plt.hist(month, rwidth=0.8);
plt.xlabel('Month');
plt.ylabel('Frequency');
